name: Vikki Green
description:
After many years as a professional designer, I am turning from the world and seeking Jesus first as my Savior, Healer, Provider and love of my life. May you also find Him as your first love and turn to Him in your life for your everything! He is the best GOD and Best Friend a person could ever have.
I love to create just as our Great Creator has and it is always humbling to be able to see what He does through me.
